Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.09,0:01:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找寻在第二界层\N某一处的真实之镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来到了十字镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们拯救了\N被东杰拉拉支配的市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.56,0:01:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要令着日夜颠倒的市镇\N恢复真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要真实之镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.66,0:01:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!\N我一定会找到的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九话\N吓一跳!\N世纪大发明镜子探测机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要制造真实之镜探测机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真简单,对我来说毫无难处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了!\N爆炸是成功之母!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊!渡,认真地跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅…不要再干这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去找真实之镜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材!\N不论什么时候也要继续修炼才是武士啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,对啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着会更加严格啊\N火美子,来下一个吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!火美子,上吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.18,0:03:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!\N不可以用眼去追看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打开心眼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼?\N近视?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心眼!心中的眼睛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多的东西\N没可能用眼睛全部看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看又看不见时便会心慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越心慌便会越看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.55,0:04:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不如索性\N闭起眼睛集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话便会感到气势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的东西也能看得见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便叫做打开心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?还活着的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了\N找真实之镜而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实之镜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆,你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我才不知道\N倒是…要吃这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!是圆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,不用客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚想吃甜食呢\N这个好像很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.95,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云?\N水在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要喝水?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了那么辣的东西\N也没事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水啊!我要找水!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.27,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会把这么重要的真实之镜\N交给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.94,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪呢,这里应该是湖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想办法啊,口要烧着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,我口内发生火警\N很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.43,0:05:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肯把那水壶的水给我\N我会很感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.97,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近水会全部向上流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水浮在天空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是这个湖的湖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近水是非常珍贵的\N你要好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么\N在口内会发生火警呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个奇怪的婆婆\N请我们吃了很辣的圆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蜜婆婆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会死掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小事便晕到\N你还是修炼不足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小桃,请问你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫渡,是为了找真实之镜\N而来到这个镇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实之镜?我曾经听过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听过?从谁人口中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.82,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N你知道了真实之镜的所在地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.95,0:07:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,而且渡他们已经出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.26,0:07:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样非常糟啊\N不可以把真实之镜交给他们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么激动\N虽然知道了所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但地方很广阔\N不是那么容易便找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们找到之前\N我们先找出来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.87,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.92,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了…\N真实之镜探测机已完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反转博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?那是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我这天才科学家\N反转博士来说这只是小儿科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且顺便已把这部法蘭擎改造了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已变成了有力量\N足以消灭龙神丸的强力魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方不同了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢材,你看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前用"钣手"\N今次是转枪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只这样…\N其实这部法蘭擎已装备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以胜过龙神丸的部件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你说\N那完成了的探测机呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就在眼前吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?好恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个眼球正是伟大的发明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本世纪的奇迹\N真实之镜探测机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭擎\N这块是真实之镜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.14,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的时候会说\N[是这个了],很惊讶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会惊讶啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.77,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这个眼球指向的方向\N便是真实之镜的所在地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立即开动它,你们等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!立即前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!那边是墙壁啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭擎发现目标后\N只会直线前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从消息中的确是那个方向呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我也去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?那是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有真实之镜的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便可以令这第二界层\N恢复原状吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.38,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那东西真的可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.87,0:10:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨!下雨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收集雨水\N这里一星期只会下一次雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以便这样收集雨水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大事件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也帮手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水不够吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,如果湖水恢复了原状\N便不用这么辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有真实之镜便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢\N可是怎样也不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,因为自从蜜婆婆\N得到了那块镜之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便变成了一个\N爱作弄人的婆婆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只鸟是你们的朋友吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是鸟!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟儿、鸟儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把真实之镜的事\N再详细点告诉我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.89,0:11:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前便传说\N这湖里有真实之镜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到它的人\N便能得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是自从多恶达\N来到这个世界之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村内的水全都飞到天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村内的人因缺水而很烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后失去了水的湖\N剩下一块镜子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜婆婆捡到了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.59,0:11:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后蜜婆婆便变成了\N很有精力爱作弄人的婆婆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.46,0:11:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此,我想到\N得到了真实之镜的蜜婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样便叫做幸福吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这回事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们找蜜婆婆把事情说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把镜子借来用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.98,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个了,是真实之镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是美丽\N何时看也是这么迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆,把镜子交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁也好\N不听我说没有好下场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样我也说不行\N你会怎样做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便会这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢,老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.58,0:13:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?这样也能\N叫我把镜子交给你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然!法蘭擎2号\N捉住那老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么?你这色鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,要吃我也不好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!还给我,那是我的镜子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!奇怪珠攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住!接住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好,火美子\N反转博士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已来了\N真实之镜是不会交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.53,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你很久了,小子\N但之前要取得真实之镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.44,0:13:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.75,0:13:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩兵捉贼吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蛋?\N竟变出这样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位还记得吗?\N小蛋是反转博士制造的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说反转博士\N是小蛋的生父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!\N儿子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人感动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.09,0:14:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的东西对法蘭擎2号来说\N便和水一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!趁现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!来吧!反转博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了吗?\N废铁机械人,法蘭擎2号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.18,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你真正的恐怖\N解放的时刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那废铁机械人\N见识你的可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多谢你惠顾(關西话)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢!多谢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你服输了吧?\N话也说不出来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.65,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是位于第一界层的\N极西的關西村用的语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?龙神丸\N你懂得说吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得输了的话便老实投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事吓不到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.71,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"你知道吗?"\N这是第二界层的名古屋市的语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"还想听吗"\N这是第四界层箱根村的语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"你没听过这样的说话吧"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.47,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是第四界层的京都市语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想听哪个地方的方言?\N随便点吧,来吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.83,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,龙神丸真厉害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样有什么厉害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说这么多话有什么作为?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!镜子怎样也无所谓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把它打得支离破碎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要示弱,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.88,0:16:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么强而有力呢\N不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题,那家伙取出武器时\N要用很多时间是他的弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!那么便全力出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.81,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了,看看这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弩箭,小心点,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样想吧,可是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改良了的不只是"钣手"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的大发明\N飞来飞去光波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.56,0:17:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生,这处很危险\N你快带她们避开一下比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,来,小桃\N火美子也来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那块镜由我拿吧,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?我觉得你拿着\N会有危险才替你拿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.54,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,真是好孩子\N你也快点到那边躲起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事想起要干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.51,0:18:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个光球\N到底是从何处飞来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?渡\N这样也是在下的徒弟吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干劲和拼劲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?龙神丸\N我不知道它会从何处攻来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!龙神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要焦急,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用眼观看的话\N看不见的东西却会跑出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心眼去看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼?说起来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以用眼睛追看\N要打开心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼…是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,渡,是这样了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他挡到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好,渡\N不愧是在下的徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.11,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.88,0:20:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.82,0:20:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心的走来竟变成这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的龙神丸,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是真实之镜了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这真实之镜不再存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个第二界层便没有救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实之镜破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.79,0:21:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.60,0:21:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么辛苦才找到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.62,0:22:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界永远也无法复原了


